a premature baby stolen from a hospital 
two weeks ago by a woman posing as a nurse was found in good 
condition monday and the mother recommended the kidnapper just 
ask the lord to forgive her for what shes done 
christopher michael jones who was born weighing only 4 pounds 
was found at a home in hot springs 50 miles away by fbi agents and 
police responding to a tip to a hot line said little rock detective 
ronnie smith the caller said the baby might be at the home he said 
acqunetta rushon smith 32 who has worked as a nurses aide in 
hot springs and has four childre was charged with kidnapping said 
hot springs police lt bobby thomas she was in jail monday night 
and bond had not been set 
