night i forgive her 
she held the baby dressed in a tiny white shirt reading 
welcome home and said he looks like 250 million wrapped up 
not just a million but 250 million he looks fantastic he looks 
like his daddy 
when she first was reunited with christopher she said i held 
him and i looked at him and i checked his fingers out and his toes 
out and his legs and his stomach and his head and everythings there 
