national geographic magazine is producing a 
publishing first in its december magazine an allholographic cover 
never before has any magazine published an entirely holographic 
cover no ink was used on the front spine or back the magazine 
reported 
its the third time however the magazine has included a 
hologram a threedimensional photo on its cover it published an 
