mikhail s gorbachevs fifth and final meeting with reagan that us 
officials say has been set for next month in washington 
the summit would give the two sides another chance to narrow the 
gap on start 
the geneva round formally ends wednesday with a ceremony in which 
the two sides will exchange copies of the start treaty draft 
kampelman 68 said it was too early to talk about whether he 
will remain chief negotiator in the bush administration 
